### MongoDB Quotes Endpoints
# These endpoints provide paginated access to quotes with various filters

# --- Variables ---
@host = http://localhost:8000
@api_key = your_api_key_here
@auth_token = Bearer {{api_key}}

### Get Recent Quotes (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/quotes/recent?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Recent Quotes (Page 2)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/quotes/recent?page=2
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Oldest Quotes (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/quotes/oldest?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Highest Value Quotes (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/quotes/highest?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Lowest Value Quotes (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/quotes/lowest?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Successful Quotes (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/quotes/successful?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Failed Quotes (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/quotes/failed?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Expired Quotes (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/quotes/expired?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Pending Quotes (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/quotes/pending?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Quotes by Product (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/quotes/by-product?product=2 Stall Restroom Trailer&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Quotes by Product - Portable Toilet (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/quotes/by-product?product=Portable Toilet&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Quote by ID
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/quotes/quote_id_here
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Sample Quote ID lookup
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/quotes/67890abcdef1234567890abc
Authorization: {{auth_token}}
